=== 付費串流計畫 ===
在2013年5月15日的Google I / O上，Google宣布將擴充Google Play音樂，增加一項名為「All Access」的付費點播音樂串流服務，讓使用者可以串流播放Google Play音樂庫中任何歌曲。 

它在美國定價為每月$9.99（如果用戶在6月30日之前註冊，每月收取的費用是$7.99）。 該服務還允許用戶將All Access音樂庫與其自身的雲端歌曲庫結合。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2013/may/15/google-launches-music-streaming-io-developer-conference|title=Google Play Music All Access: search giant launches rival to Spotify|accessdate=2014-08-13|date=2013-05-16|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|first1=Dominic|last1=Rushe|first2=Charles|last2=Arthur|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112004308/http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2013/may/15/google-launches-music-streaming-io-developer-conference|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2013/5/15/4334790/google-music-all-access-hands-on-versus-spotify-rdio/in/4095431|title=Google Play Music All Access hands-on: should you switch from Spotify or Rdio?|accessdate=2014-08-13|date=2013-05-15|last=D'Orazio|first=Dante|work=The Verge|publisher=Vox Media|archive-date=2016-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107120904/http://www.theverge.com/2013/5/15/4334790/google-music-all-access-hands-on-versus-spotify-rdio/in/4095431|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2013/5/15/4335102/google-hints-at-play-music-for-other-platforms-youtube-integration-likely/in/4095431|title=Google hints at Play Music for other platforms, says YouTube integration 'likely'|accessdate=2014-08-13|date=2014-05-15|last=Patel|first=Nilay|work=The Verge|publisher=Vox Media|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629055954/https://www.theverge.com/2013/5/15/4335102/google-hints-at-play-music-for-other-platforms-youtube-integration-likely/in/4095431|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.engadget.com/2013/05/15/google-play-music-all-access-officially-unveiled/|title=Google launches All Access music-streaming service in the US: $9.99 monthly fee|accessdate=2014-08-13|date=2014-05-15|last=Silbert|first=Sarah|work=Engadget|publisher=AOL|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609013900/http://www.engadget.com/2013/05/15/google-play-music-all-access-officially-unveiled/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年11月12日，Google子公司YouTube宣布推出「音樂鑰匙(Music Key)」測試服務，這是一項新的高級服務，它包含在All Access之中，可在YouTube上無廣告的音樂影片串流。 

此外，兩個平台在付費串流的方面進行了整合：兩者都提供Google Play音樂推薦和YouTube音樂視頻無廣告串流服務。<ref name="verge-musickey">{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2014/11/12/7201969/youtube-music-key-new-subscription-service|title=YouTube announces plans for a subscription music service|accessdate=2014-11-12|website=The Verge|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107025556/https://www.theverge.com/2014/11/12/7201969/youtube-music-key-new-subscription-service|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="variety-musickey">{{cite news|url=http://variety.com/2014/digital/news/youtube-launches-music-key-subscription-service-with-more-than-30-million-songs-1201354498/|script-title=en:YouTube Launches ‘Music Key’ Subscription Service with More Than 30 Million Songs|last=Spangler|first=Todd|date=2014-11-12|accessdate=2014-11-12|website=Variety|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106160813/https://variety.com/2014/digital/news/youtube-launches-music-key-subscription-service-with-more-than-30-million-songs-1201354498/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

「YouTube Red」於2015年10月28日作為「音樂鑰匙(Music Key)」的正式版本重新推出並擴大其服務範圍：所有YouTube視頻接提供無廣告的訪問權限而不限於音樂類型，還與知名YouTuber 合作製作優質內容。<ref name="verge-youtubered">{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/10/21/9566973/youtube-red-ad-free-offline-paid-subscription-service|title=Red Dawn: An inside look at YouTube’s new ad-free subscription service|accessdate=2015-10-21|publisher=Vox Media|website=The Verge|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124115454/https://www.theverge.com/2015/10/21/9566973/youtube-red-ad-free-offline-paid-subscription-service|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

現時「All Access」付費服務訂閱價格為每月價格9.99美元，包含YouTube Red和Google Play音樂串流服務。

2015年12月，Google開始提供「Google Play 音樂」家庭計劃，最多可容納6位家庭成員，每月US $ 14.99。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://officialandroid.blogspot.ca/2015/12/google-play-music-now-playing-for-your.html|title=Google Play Music: Now playing for your family|accessdate=2016-01-06|date=2015-12-09|last=Eunice|first=Kim|work=[[Google|Google]]|publisher=Android Official Blog|archive-date=2016-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160417155053/http://officialandroid.blogspot.ca/2015/12/google-play-music-now-playing-for-your.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

家庭成員能將他們的訂閱層級升級到家庭計劃，允許家庭組的成員同時串流音樂，每人在最多 10 部裝置上使用「Google Play 音樂」。 

家庭計劃目前僅在澳大利亞，巴西，加拿大，法國，德國，愛爾蘭，日本，英國和美國可用，且只能使用Android設備建立。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://support.google.com/googleplay/answer/6317786|title=Google Play Music family plan|accessdate=2016-01-06|work=[[Google|Google]]|publisher=Google Play Help|archive-date=2017-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170331121856/https://support.google.com/googleplay/answer/6317786|dead-url=no}}</ref>

